<section class="testimonial py-5" id="testimonial">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row ">
            <div class="alert alert-primary" role="alert">
                <h4 class="alert-heading">Online Registration</h4>
                <p>
                    SOUTHERN PHILIPPINE TECHNICAL COLLEGE (SPTC) OF KORONADAL, INC.
                    ONLINE ENROLLMENT AND SURVEY ON PREFERRED ALTERNATIVE DELIVERY MODE (Learning Modalities) SCHOOL YEAR 2020-2021.
                </p>
                <hr>
                <p class="mb-0">
                    In the midst of the Covid 19 pandemic, the approach to education shall be anchored on the premise that education must continue and therefore it is everybody’s responsibility to ensure that flexible learning is delivered whether face to face or virtual approach with or without physically going to school.
